cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper is about automatic image categorization using deep convolutional neural networks (DCNNs). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms and feature engineering, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of multi-media data, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
